{"tid":2097952,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【新冠肺炎】62歲患者勃起4小時止不住，醫生揭病毒可誘發「陰莖異常勃起症」。","createTime":"2020-07-07T06:55:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-07T07:54:26.000Z","uid":54337,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"be00161289988948e392dad23aaf3c9ae12a5981","tid":2097952,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T06:55:35.000Z","msg":"【新冠肺炎】62歲患者勃起4小時止不住，醫生揭病毒可誘發「陰莖異常勃起症」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://medicalinspire.com/web/posts/53984\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedicalinspire.com%2Fweb%2Fposts%2F53984&d=uYDAXyhVPN7xTSuHIXBXEkkSG0DzaVerHR9pE4rwCb4%3D&h=9da1bfa3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://medicalinspire.com/web/posts/53984</a><br />\n<br />\n疫情不斷升溫，全球新冠肺炎確診人數突破1,100萬，隨著各地學者努力不懈分析病毒，人類對新冠病毒的了解與日俱增，越來越多研究發現新冠病毒對人體的遺禍遠不只影響呼吸系統。近期，法國一名62歲的男患者在治療期間，其下體竟離奇「勃起」長達4小時，醫生推斷該情況或揭示新冠肺炎可引致血栓問題，繼而引發「陰莖異常勃起症」（priapism）。有關病例報告日前已刊登於《美國急診醫學雜誌》（The American Journal of Emergency Medicine）。<br />\n<br />\n新冠肺炎造成血栓致陰莖異常勃起症<br />\n該名62歲的男確診者須靠呼吸器輔助呼吸，他染疫後入住法國凡爾賽中心醫院（Centre Hospitalier de Versailles），院方為他進行身體檢查時，患者出現原因未明的「陰莖異常勃起症」，該病症在病人身上原來早已持續一段時間未有改善。<br />\n<br />\n報告指，患者兩側海綿體處於堅硬（rigid）狀態，陰莖頭則處於鬆軟（flaccid）狀態，顯示血液栓塞在陰莖勃起腔內，相信是低血流性陰莖異常勃起症。醫生見狀隨即為患者冰敷以緩和症狀，惟其勃起狀態仍持續長達4小時，即使患者當時已被鎮靜亦依然相當痛苦。醫生最終以針筒為其陰莖放血，結果竟抽出深色血栓，報告推斷是由於新冠肺炎可併發引起血栓問題。"},{"pid":"c797f74274e04fafa9351bcc0a9af6c96f3aa605","tid":2097952,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T06:56:05.000Z","msg":"可對性功能造成永久性傷害<br />\n陰莖異常勃起症，言即陰莖因血管堵塞而無法回復自然疲軟狀態，當血液不斷被泵送進下體，長此下去部分組織將受到永久性傷害，導致日後難以勃起。<br />\n<br />\n醫生隨後為患者注射藥物並給予防血栓藥物，出院後逐漸康復，且再未出現異常勃起的問題。學者指出，血栓症狀在新冠肺炎患者身上極其常見，但是次病例是首宗血塊栓塞在陰莖導致「陰莖異常勃起症」的病例。<br />\n<br />\nSource：美國急診醫學雜誌"},{"pid":"9b89e7e5061b0b227ce3d5a755a65459ca7b6946","tid":2097952,"uid":132587,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T06:56:49.000Z","msg":"班雞蟲即刻衝去大陸感染武肺先<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43982b1836cc180e38fd4ecb9843552ab113512a","tid":2097952,"uid":199456,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T06:59:17.000Z","msg":"想做巨根 可以先染病<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43076740620cd3e8df206bb513b4de3f9f2bb641","tid":2097952,"uid":60057,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T07:00:14.000Z","msg":"可以有人生最後一次勃起"},{"pid":"a1c42ff06a96768096722f32d7a98f8acde5addc","tid":2097952,"uid":199456,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T07:06:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Eqxffir.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEqxffir.jpg&h=afadf611&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"70203bda109ccd07069a1027aa26a8ed9bef9873","tid":2097952,"uid":2267,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T07:08:38.000Z","msg":"偉哥係咪可以有新藥方研究？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a3b5cf172d6d65e4a02aa6ec5d4bd043ff2b58b","tid":2097952,"uid":28121,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T07:24:26.000Z","msg":"立場張圖笑到我<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/Layer201_0Bjev_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2FLayer201_0Bjev_1200x0.png&h=17049798&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"804f6b11334f7cea7780dbeb46facc69a85311fc","tid":2097952,"uid":251852,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a1c42ff06a96768096722f32d7a98f8acde5addc","tid":2097952,"uid":199456,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T07:06:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Eqxffir.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEqxffir.jpg&h=afadf611&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T07:48:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"363f6e93a019c233d2b77e4ea3b662a8db203967","tid":2097952,"uid":62749,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T07:49:06.000Z","msg":"武漢壯陽毒"},{"pid":"654aa8a4a62b3596a49412763e35fabfeb9979d0","tid":2097952,"uid":188334,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"9b89e7e5061b0b227ce3d5a755a65459ca7b6946","tid":2097952,"uid":132587,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T06:56:49.000Z","msg":"班雞蟲即刻衝去大陸感染武肺先<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T07:49:53.000Z","msg":"之後隔離十四日打飛機？"},{"pid":"bbbfa7bf02911aa994871d8c3d8fb747d5c577f7","tid":2097952,"uid":126226,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T07:52:52.000Z","msg":"射精解唔解脱到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5176f6fcee9792c478cf61616467aaa922c3a2d","tid":2097952,"uid":158457,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T07:54:26.000Z","msg":"武漢肺炎變種到有春藥成份<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}